{"title":"我为人民上大学","authors":["董立英"],"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":2,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为人民上大学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农学系学员　董立英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村头喜鹊叫喳喳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风引路上“农大”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳边回荡乡亲们的嘱托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头铭记老支书的话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学校赠我两件宝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝书四卷，银锄一把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社来社去当农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早把决心下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举“抗大”的旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大凌河畔安新家；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走“共大”的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹰嘴山下意气风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级斗争的战场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经得起风浪摔打；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学大寨的熔炉中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炼就一身钢铁骨架。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常念故乡山和水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀祖国想天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反修防修意志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的宏图心中画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈着坚定的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着漫天的朝霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农送我上大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誓在农村把根扎！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}